  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "Indexed\nfolder 90 - 057\n-12-\n\nview, expressed in the E.B. macro article on pantheism, that we are cells within an enormous brain or brain-like entity. (That was, after all, my contention in VALIS.) But I have a detailed understanding --or detailed conception-- of how it works, and I really did arrive at that independently of Whitehead. My conception, which I arrived at suddenly last Wednesday night, is based in the final analysis on my encounter with and apperception of VALIS back in 1974. Now, ",
